  '[{"author":"Default","content":"Hi [Name], this is [Your Name]\nThanks for taking the call just now! 😊\n\nAs mentioned, you''ve qualified for our financial literacy session which allows you to redeem a $20 Capitaland voucher.\n\nWe''ll help you redeem it through a quick zoom session where we''ll share some helpful tips on how to grow your money faster than just saving in the bank as well 💰\n\nI''ve scheduled your session for [Confirmed Date & Time].\nJust reply \"Yes\" to confirm this timing and we''re all set!\n\nLooking forward to chatting with you then! 👍\n\nAs a bonus, you will also get these resources after the consultation\n\n![Free Ultimate Guide to Adulting](/scripts/free-adulting-guide-promo.png)\n\n![Free Ultimate Guide to Investing](/scripts/free-investing-guide-promo.png)\n\nWould sometime next Saturday or Sunday at 10am or 2pm work for you?"}]'::jsonb,
